\title{
Polyfit add-on to DESeq}
\description{
implementation the Polyfit add-on to DESeq described in the paper 
"Improved error estimates for the analysis of differential expression from RNA-seq data"
}
\details{
\tabular{ll}{
Package: \tab Polyfit\cr
